snippet.title: Syndicate - Atari Jaguar
snippet.description:
Syndicate is one of those games I always wanted to play on my Jaguar when I first got one as a kid.
I unfortunately never did get it until recently.
I was unsure exactly what type of game it is, but from what I just played, it's one that could take a lot of time.
It seems slow-moving, though that could very well be because I was only on the first mission.
Once I figured things out a bit, though, it went a little smoother.
I'd definitely give the game some more time to get into it and really get the controls down pat.
